# ${NAME}

Minimal Express server scaffolded by phi.

## Install

```sh
phi install
```

## Run

```sh
phi do dev      # auto-restart on file changes (Node 18.11+)
phi do start    # plain run
```

Server listens on `http://localhost:3000` by default. Set `PORT` to override.

## Routes

- `GET /` — hello-world response
- `GET /health` — process uptime + status
